349
00:27:15,250 --> 00:27:18,207
And both,
she and Katrina don't recognize you.

350
00:27:22,208 --> 00:27:24,249
- How is it going, Kundan?
- Hello, aunty.

351
00:27:24,458 --> 00:27:26,499
